inputs.description: A collection of arguments for invoking getNamespace.

outputs.description: A collection of values returned by getNamespace.

adminUsername.description: The username of the administrator for the first database created in the namespace.

arn.description: Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the Redshift Serverless Namespace.

dbName.description: The name of the first database created in the namespace.

defaultIamRoleArn.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the IAM role to set as a default in the namespace. When specifying `default_iam_role_arn`, it also must be part of `iam_roles`.

iamRoles.description: A list of IAM roles to associate with the namespace.

id.description: The provider-assigned unique ID for this managed resource.

kmsKeyId.description: The ARN of the Amazon Web Services Key Management Service key used to encrypt your data.

logExports.description: The types of logs the namespace can export. Available export types are `userlog`, `connectionlog`, and `useractivitylog`.
